@OrderingApi_HostAddress = http://localhost:5198
@Bearer_Token = BURAYA_ACCESS_TOKEN_YAPIŞTIRIN

### Herkese açık
GET {{OrderingApi_HostAddress}}/api/orders/public
Accept: application/json

###
### Tüm siparişler (Admin)
GET {{OrderingApi_HostAddress}}/api/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{Bearer_Token}}
Accept: application/json

###
### Benim siparişlerim (Admin veya User)
GET {{OrderingApi_HostAddress}}/api/orders/my
Authorization: Bearer {{Bearer_Token}}
Accept: application/json

###
### Sipariş oluştur (Admin veya User)
POST {{OrderingApi_HostAddress}}/api/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{Bearer_Token}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

